  "bodyText": "Pricing\nContact\nLog in\nSign up\nCreate lyric videos\nwith AI in minutes.\nFree preview · Fully customizable · No templates\nUpload your song to get an instant preview\nUpload your song\nMax 100MB · Formats: MP3, WAV, FLAC, AAC, OGG, M4A\nFree preview\n\nCreate and edit your video before purchasing. No credit card required.\n\nFully customizable\n\nChange the story, art style, fonts, scenes, and timing in our real-time editor.\n\n90+ languages\n\nOur AI will transcribe the lyrics of your song automatically.\n\nSee what you can create\nReal videos made with LyricEdits\nThe Giants Are Marching Home\nAutomatic Ape\nBubbles\nBiffy Clyro\nFilla On Ets\nFerran Saurina\nTease Her\nStrange Fiction\nÚltimo Aliento\nDaeria\nBad Chick\nThe Madpix Project\nUpload your song\nYOU ALREADY\nKNOW THIS\nFEELING.\n\nThe feeling of finishing THE SONG.\nAfter hours of composing, writing, recording, mixing, and iterating.\n\nYou’re excited to show it to the world. But you need a video.\nA music video worthy of your song.\n\nAnd suddenly, you realize:\n\n“I need a budget. I need time. I need to find people to help me.”\n\nIn that moment, you feel stuck.\n\nLyricEdits exists for that moment.\n\nIt was built by musicians, for musicians.\nWe’ve been there, we get it.\n\nOur AI helps bring your vision to life.\n\nNOT A MAGIC BUTTON\n\nThis is not a template. It’s a real music video workflow, available to every artist.\n\nAI + HUMAN CREATIVITY\n\nWe designed a tool that merges AI with human creativity. From your idea to a finished video, all in one place.\n\nCREATIVITY IS IN\nYOUR HANDS.\n\nCustomize every detail, or keep it simple and move fast.\n\nUpload your song\nThe AI Lyric Video Maker for Music\n\nLyricEdits is an AI lyric video maker designed specifically for music.\nMost AI video tools are built for ads and reels. LyricEdits is built for songs.\n\nStart with an AI-generated video, then make it yours.\n\nCustomize any detail in our real-time editor: story, characters, fonts, images, videos, colors, lyrics and pace.\n\nNo video editing experience required.\n\nLog in to access the editor\n\nHow to Make a Lyric Video with AI\nPlay\nUsed by Music Creators and Labels Worldwide\n\nArtists all over the world are already sharing their music this way.\n\n90,000+\nlyric videos created with LyricEdits\n20,000+\nmusic creators and labels using LyricEdits\n85+\nlanguages across the world\nExport to Your Favorite Editor\n\nStart in LyricEdits. Finish in the tools you already use.\n\nCreate your lyric video in minutes, then export to DaVinci Resolve, Premiere Pro, or Final Cut Pro for advanced editing.\n\nFor filmmakers\n\nTry it for free\n\nSee your video before paying anything.\nNo stress. No surprises.\n\nFree preview\nNo watermarks\nYou keep all rights\nCancel anytime\n\nUpload your song to start\n\nFAQ\n\nFeel free to contact us for any questions or doubts.\n\nWe'll be more than happy to help you!\n\nCan I post the video to YouTube or other platforms?\n\nYes! As long as you own the rights to the song or have permission from the artist, you can post the video on YouTube, Instagram, TikTok, or any other platform.\nNOTE: some platforms may require you a percentage of moving images in the video, so please check their requirements.\n\nCan I use the video for commercial purposes?\nCan I upload a song on behalf of another artist?\nHow do you generate the videos?\nWhich AI models do you use?\n\nYou've finished your song.\n\nLet people see it.\nLet people feel it.\n\nCreate your lyric video now:\n\nUPLOAD YOUR SONG\n\nMade by musicians for musicians.\n\nFollow us on\n\nAll rights reserved © 2024 - 2026\n\nRESOURCES\nHome\nPricing\nUses\nBlog\nDiscount\nCOMPANY\nAbout us\nAffiliates\nContact\nPRODUCTS\nAI Lyric Video Maker\nAI Video Creation from Lyrics\nLyric Video Creator\nLyric Video Editor\nLyric Video Generator AI\nLEGAL\nTerms of Service\nPrivacy Policy\nCookie Usage\n\nThis site uses essential cookies to properly operate and tracking cookies—disabled by default—to understand how you interact with the site.\n\nAccept all\nReject all\nManage preferences",
